== Purpose ==

Similarly to the command ''Image {{arrow}} Color {{arrow}} RGB split'', this plugin unmixes an RGB image produced by subtractive mixing (inks, histological dyes) into separate channels correspondig to up to 3 determined colors. This is useful e.g. to do pigment separation. 

== Documentation ==

See [http://www.mecourse.com/landinig/software/cdeconv/cdeconv.html Gabriel Landini webpage].

